OL,3,CMother of Baby P was recalled to
OL,4,Cprison after failing to disclose
OL,5,Crelationship
OL,7,FThe mother of Baby P, who died after
OL,8,Fmonths of abuse, was recalled to
OL,9,Fprison last year after she started a
OL,10,Frelationship with a man she met online
OL,11,Fwithout telling officials supervising
OL,12,Fher, a parole hearing has been told.
OL,14,FTracey Connelly was jailed at the Old
OL,15,FBailey in 2009 for causing or allowing
OL,16,Fthe death of her 17-month-old son
OL,17,FPeter at their home in Tottenham,
OL,18,Fnorth London, on August 3 2007.
