OL,7,FThis is her first review since
OL,8,FConnelly, now in her 40s, was recalled
OL,9,Fto prison for a second time in August
OL,10,Flast year for breaching her licence
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,FHer parole hearing, livestreamed by
OL,14,Fvideo feed on Wednesday, heard the
OL,15,Fsituation "closely mirrored" that of
OL,16,Fher first recall and when she was in
OL,17,Fcustody following her return to
OL,18,Fprison, when she also developed other
OL,19,Fintimate relationships.
