OL,7,FThe hearing was told by her prison
OL,8,Foffender manager (POM) that Connelly
OL,9,Fhad deleted material from her phone to
OL,10,Favoid officials finding out about her
OL,11,Frelationship, which led to her second
OL,12,Frecall.
OL,14,FPanel chairwoman Sally Allbeury said:
OL,15,F"The 2013 panel considered there to be
OL,16,Fa major risk in the context of Ms
OL,17,FConnelly developing an intimate
OL,18,Frelationship where she prioritises a
OL,19,Fpartner's needs and her own needs over
OL,20,Fthose of children. Subsequent panels
OL,21,Fhave had the same concerns."
