OL,5,Crelationship
OL,7,FConnelly had failed to disclose to
OL,8,Fsocial services that others were
OL,9,Fliving in the house after her partner
OL,10,Fand his brother moved into the home,
OL,11,Fand a Parole Board hearing in 2013
OL,12,Fsaid she had been keen to preserve her
OL,13,Fintimate relationships at all costs.
OL,15,FKnown publicly as Baby P, Peter
OL,16,Fsuffered more than 50 injuries,
OL,17,Fdespite being on the at-risk register
OL,18,Fand receiving 60 visits from social
OL,19,Fworkers, police officers and health
OL,20,Fprofessionals over eight months.
