OL,7,FGiving evidence to the hearing on
OL,8,FWednesday, her POM was asked why
OL,9,FConnelly did not disclose the most
OL,10,Frecent relationship, which she
OL,11,Freplied: "From what we've discussed
OL,12,Fthere was fear of being judged."
