OL,7,FAsked about progress she has made on
OL,8,Funderstanding why Connelly keeps
OL,9,Fgetting into the same patterns of
OL,10,Fbehaviour, referring to unhealthy
OL,11,Frelationships, the official said:
OL,12,F"Yeah... how she views herself. It's
OL,13,Fvery difficult for her in the
OL,14,Fcommunity. She had this relationship
OL,15,Fand it made her feel nice and she
OL,16,Fdidn't want to lose that."
