OL,7,FThe panel chairwoman also said
OL,8,FConnelly is "perfectly entitled" to
OL,9,Fget involved in any kind of
OL,10,Frelationship she wants as long as she
OL,11,Ftells people about it, and asked what
OL,12,Fis stopping her from disclosing them.
OL,14,FThe POM said: "We all understand what
OL,15,Fshe got from... that relationship is
OL,16,Fmaking her feel good about herself.
