OL,7,F"If she then disclosed at that point
OL,8,Feither probation will say you can't
OL,9,Fhave the relationship... or we need to
OL,10,Fdisclose to him, which leads to a fear
OL,11,Fof 'once he knows who I am he won't
OL,12,Fwant me'."
OL,14,FThe prison official recommended
OL,15,FConnelly for re-release with a
OL,16,Fmanagement plan.
