OL,7,FThey said based on discussions with
OL,8,FConnelly, she has got an awareness of
OL,9,Fwhat an unhealthy relationship looks
OL,10,Flike and what the warning signs might
OL,11,Fbe.
OL,13,FAsked if Connelly believes she would
OL,14,Fbe a future risk to a child, the POM
OL,15,Fadded she is "very aware" of risk
OL,16,Fassessments and has never sought to
OL,17,Fminimise that in discussions.
