OL,7,FConnelly had admitted the offence of
OL,8,Fcausing or allowing the death of her
OL,9,Fson and was handed a sentence of
OL,10,Fimprisonment for public protection
OL,11,Fwith a minimum term of five years.
OL,13,FHer then boyfriend, Steven Barker, and
OL,14,Fhis brother, Jason Owen, were
OL,15,Fconvicted of the same crime.
OL,17,FEarlier in the hearing, the chairwoman
OL,18,Fsaid the panel has heard "extremely
OL,19,Fmoving" victim statements from the
OL,20,Fchild's loved ones.
