OL,7,F"There can be no doubt that Peter's
OL,8,Fdeath has caused lifelong harm to
OL,9,Fthose who loved him," Ms Allbeury said.
OL,11,FThe Parole Board will publish a
OL,12,Fredacted decision of Connelly's case
OL,13,Fwhen a decision is made, usually
OL,14,Fwithin 14 days of the hearing.
